nodes.text: Don't Get All Mushy is an article written by Nathanael Tripp and published by Wizards of the Coast on February 24, 2005.

The article details the use of the "Don't Get All Mushy" card in the Star Wars Trading Card Game and the title stems from a line spoken by Han Solo in The Empire Strikes Back: "Well, don't get all mushy on me. So long, Princess."
